original_title: 19歳の冒険AV DEBUT ど田舎はヤルことがない！暇が嫌いな女子大生
overview: The story of a country girl's AV debut in Tokyo- "The countryside is free anyway, and I long for Tokyo, which is everything. I was interested in naughty things, so I wondered if I could live here if I became an AV actress." A curious girl who speaks while shining. It seems that it still takes a little courage to get naked in public ... Shyly take off for the first time & first SEX! The great adventure of 19-year-old'Welcome-chan', who is loved like Pomeranian, has just begun.
title: The Adventure of A 19-Year Old Making Her AV Debut: There's Nothing to Do Out in the Sticks! A College Girl Who Hates Being Bored: Erina Oka
